project_descr: Helping citizens get an easy, friendly, equitable and corruption-free access to services provided by central and local level institutions.

outputs.output_descr: The overall objective of this project is to contribute to the achievement of the country’s long-term goals related to the EU integration processes and fight against corruption. It is helping the citizens get an easy, friendly, equitable and corruption-free access to services provided by central and local level institutions.
